data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. WOW!! ZERO DOWN USDA LOAN AVAILABLE For This Property! IF You Have Been Dreaming of Owning A BEAUTIFULLY UPDATED HOME w/ Your Very Own MINI FARM ON JUST UNDER 5 ACRES, This Property Is For YOU!! SO Many UPDATES In This Spacious and Open 3 Bedroom, 2 Full Bath Home Including Waterproof Laminate Flooring Throughout. The Updated Kitchen Includes a Walk-In Pantry, All Appliances, Newer Cabinets, Lighting, Granite Counters, Deep Sink, Faucet, and LARGE Island with Overhang for Barstools. The Great Room and Dining Room Were Updated with Trendy Metal Tin Paneling and Lead to the Large Deck Off the Back! All 3 Bedrooms Are Good Sizes with Walk-In Closets; The Primary Bedroom with Its Own Full Bathroom. The Hall Bath Has Been Fully Updated. Inside Laundry Room Includes the Washer, Dryer, and Deep Freezer.  ON THE PROPERTY, You Will Find Enough Storage for All Your Recreation! The Newer 2022 30x30 Garage Has Electric and Can Fit RVs, Boats, Cars, etc. and Includes Shelving and a Workspace. There are 3 Additional Smithbilt Sheds, One with Electric.  BRING YOUR HORSES, CHICKENS, GOATS, and any other livestock you desire! There is a Barn with 3 Divisible Stalls, a Chicken Coop with Electric, and Conveniently, a 2nd Well for Animals/Outside Watering. The Front Well has a Newer Water softener and Purification System 2022 ($6000). Roof and AC Replaced in 2019.... LOCATION Just 10 minutes from Town, the property goes West to the Walk-In-Water Creek and is Conveniently Located just off of State Road 60 East of Lake Wales. River Ranch is about 15 minutes to the East and Beautiful VERO BEACH LESS Than ONE Hour Away. Animals may be conveyed with home. Call today and make Your DREAMS COME TRUE!
